'''Marko Todorovi<U+0107>''' ([[Montenegrin alphabet|Montenegrin Cyrillic]]: <U+041C><U+0430><U+0440><U+043A><U+043E> <U+0422><U+043E><U+0434><U+043E><U+0440><U+043E><U+0432><U+0438><U+045B>; born April 19, 1992) is a Montenegrin professional [[basketball]] player for [[FC Barcelona B<U+00E0>squet|FC Barcelona]] of the [[Liga ACB|Spanish ACB League]]. He is a 6&nbsp;ft 10<U+00BE> in (2.10 m) tall [[power forward (basketball)|power forward]]-[[center (basketball)|center]].

==Professional career==
Todorovi<U+0107> played basketball at the junior level with the youth teams of KK Joker in Montenegro and Joventut Badalona in Spain. He played with Joventut Badalona's second team, [[CB Prat Joventut|Prat Joventut]], in the [[LEB Plata|Spanish 3rd Division]], from 2010 to 2012. He also played with the senior men's team of [[Joventut Badalona]], in the [[Spanish ACB League]], from 2011 to 2012.

He joined [[FC Barcelona B<U+00E0>squet|Barcelona B<U+00E0>squet]] before the start of the 2012-13 season.<ref>[http://www.euroleague.net/news/i/99104/180/fc-barcelona-regal-gets-young-prospect-todorovic Euroleague.net FC Barcelona Regal gets young prospect Todorovic.]</ref>

On June 27, 2013, Todorovic was drafted 45th overall by the [[Portland Trail Blazers]] of the [[National Basketball Association]]. On July 10, 2013, the Trail Blazers traded his rights to the [[Houston Rockets]] as part of a trade for [[Thomas Robinson (basketball)|Thomas Robinson]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.iamatrailblazersfan.com/PressReleaseDisplay/tabid/297/itemId/3866/Default.aspx|title=TRAIL BLAZERS ACQUIRE THOMAS ROBINSON FROM HOUSTON|work=NBA.com|date=July 10, 2013}}</ref>

==Montenegrin national team==
Todorovi<U+0107> was a member of the junior national teams of Montenegro. He played at the [[2011 FIBA Europe Under-20 Championship]].

==Awards and accomplishments==
* [[LEB Plata|Spanish 3rd Division]] MVP: [[2011<U+2013>12 LEB Plata season|2012]]
* [[Spanish Basketball Cup|Spanish Cup]] Champion: [[Copa del Rey de Baloncesto 2012<U+2013>13|2013]]

